<Link id="l01493" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1493"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Get pointer to Communications Vector Table (CVT).</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01494" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1494"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The pointer is located at offset 16 of the Prefixed Save Area (PSA).</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01495" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1495"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// It is stored as 31 bit pointer and will be zero-extended to 64 bit.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01496" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1496"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">int</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> &#42;StartToCVTOffset = </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">reinterpret&#95;cast&lt;</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">int</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> &#42;</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">&gt;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">(0x10);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01497" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1497"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Since its stored as a 31-bit pointer, get the 4 bytes from the start</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01498" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1498"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// of address.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01499" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1499"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">int</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> ReadValue = &#42;StartToCVTOffset;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01500" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1500"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Explicitly clear the high order bit.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01501" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1501"><span class="doxyHighlight">  ReadValue = (ReadValue &amp; 0x7FFFFFFF);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01502" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1502"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">char</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> &#42;CVT = </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">reinterpret&#95;cast&lt;</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">char</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> &#42;</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">&gt;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">(ReadValue);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01503" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1503"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The model number is located in the CVT prefix at offset -6 and stored as</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01504" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1504"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// signless packed decimal.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01505" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1505"><span class="doxyHighlight">  uint16&#95;t <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/amdgpu/vgprindexmode/#a9afd95476c40096a5898ba0f06370b3a">Id</a> = &#42;(uint16&#95;t &#42;)&amp;CVT&#91;-6&#93;;</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01508" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1508"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Check for vector support. It&#39;s stored in field CVTFLAG5 (offset 244),</span></CodeLine>
